msgctxt "84_Middle-aged Man"
msgid "I haven't seen that girl from Sky Finance around lately."
msgstr "No vi a la chica del Sky Finance últimamente."

msgctxt "96_Middle-aged Man"
msgid "I used to see her walking to work every day with a\r\n"
"bento in her hand and a grin on her face."
msgstr "Solía verla caminar al trabajo cada día junto a\r\n"
"un bento en la mano y muy contenta."

msgctxt "108_Middle-aged Man"
msgid "That big, healthy smile of hers always cheered me up...\r\n"
"Now I really miss her."
msgstr "Esa gran alegría que emitía siempre animaba...\r\n"
"Ahora realmente la extraño."

